title: Sri Lankan Chicken & Veggie Curry with Basmati Rice & Toasted Coconut
description: This colourful curry has everything you never knew you needed - with tender chicken breast mixed with
flavourful spices, creamy coconut and veggies, it’s the ultimate in Sri Lankan-style cuisine.

